<P>English Housewifry. EXEMPLIFIED In above four Hundred and Fifty RECEIPTS, Giving DIRECTIONS in most Parts of COOKERY; and how to prepare various Sorts of
<LIST>
<ITEM>SOOPS,</ITEM>
<ITEM>MADE-DISHES,</ITEM>
