With CUTS for the orderly placing the DISHES and COURSES; also Bills of Fare for every Month in the Year; and an Alphabetical INDEX of the Whole.</P>
<P>A BOOK necessary for Mistresses of Families, higher and lower Women Servants, and confined to Things USEFUL, SUBSTANTIAL and SPLENDID, and cal|culated for the Preservation of HEALTH, and upon the Measures of FRUGALITY, being the Result of thirty Years <HI>Practice</HI> and <HI>Experience.</HI></P>
